==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The normal state of a [[diploid]] [[eukaryotic]] [[cell]] or individual which has two members of a pair of [[homologous]] [[chromosomes]] in each [[nucleus]].  A [[normal]] chromosome is represented [[twice]] in a single cell.

